No patient-level data
---------------------

ChronoMedKG contains no patient-level data. All onset-age information is
literature-level (aggregated clinical descriptions from PubMed/PMC articles,
Orphadata disease epidemiology, or HPOA disease-level annotations). No
de-identified electronic health records, imaging, or other protected health
information is included.

Clinician rating data (Section 4.3 of the paper) was collected from
consenting physicians and contains no patient information; it is reported
in anonymised aggregate form only.

